msgid "Server Maintenance"
msgstr "Maintenance du serveur"

#: ../../hosting/maintenance/index.rst:9
msgid ""
"This section covers how to maintain Parsec Server up to date, and how to "
"backup and restore the PostgreSQL database and the Object Storage."
msgstr ""
"Cette section explique comment maintenir Parsec Server à jour, ainsi que "
"comment sauvegarder et restaurer la base de données PostgreSQL et le "
"Stockage Objets."
